    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/e468b4aa0bd92efc21494186d1061809.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/2d1e07901b594bc52b74889b66210f1f.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/2d1e07901b594bc52b74889b66210f1f.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/2d1e07901b594bc52b74889b66210f1f.mp4?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Travel the universe as a hired gun, explore distant planets and fight dangerous enemies in this action-packed roguelite. Complete many different missions on your quest for finding a cure against the taint.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/02447c8f30215acede182395be2b7389.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/9f4afa9508ba79012b236a38a4854d41.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/9f4afa9508ba79012b236a38a4854d41.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/9f4afa9508ba79012b236a38a4854d41.mp4?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore dark caverns and deep abysses, illuminate them using the liquid flux running through your veins, also serving as a powerful weapon against all sorts of unwelcome guests. But beware, as it will drain your lifeforce.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/bbb58fc3c1c2958b1790676d4ec74f8c.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/d0885b983ea963cf4c32dca6f5131042.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/d0885b983ea963cf4c32dca6f5131042.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/d0885b983ea963cf4c32dca6f5131042.mp4?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dig through randomly generated caves and destroy entire dungeons on a pixel basis. Find and extract valuable resources that will help you to gear up for whatever lurks deeper in the caverns.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/4c6af940b911bec854d96899c0b3f13c.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.mp4?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Assemble and upgrade complex weaponry using the arms generator from your handy drop pod which can produce hundreds of different combinations.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/81cd113b6ec97908e1a8b6d5f93198c7.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.mp4?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Visit the Space-Bar, haven to various criminals, bounty hunters and bandits. Meet and befriend all sorts of creatures, contractors and private quest givers in this shady interstellar hideout.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/4e4404c341252f09b0b2f40f84c0d6f0.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.poster.avif?t=1673616513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868350/extras/f916f3e2d4a3aff69d1f488ce3432d4e.webm?t=1673616513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/